{"tid":499741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲囚犯可啪啪啪！獎勵表現良好者　供單人房開房間","createTime":"2017-12-15T06:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T14:39:36.000Z","uid":22675,"like":148,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"44dd50026a7b2c115de4aee60848580e626d3018","tid":499741,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:58:34.000Z","msg":"男性專區<br />\n澳洲囚犯可啪啪啪！獎勵表現良好者　供單人房開房間<br />\n2017-12-15<br />\n<br />\n澳洲首都地區及維多利亞州的政府允許表現良好的囚犯，可在單人房間裡與伴侶發生性行為。（圖／達志／示意圖）<br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n澳洲政府為了降低囚犯日後再犯的可能性，能在出獄後快速融入家庭生活，竟出奇招，獎勵表現良好的囚犯能與伴侶在特別準備的單人房裡發生性行為。<br />\n<br />\n據澳洲《太陽先驅報》報導，維多利亞州、澳洲首都領地這兩處的監獄允許表現優異的囚犯申請這項獎勵，不過有幾項限制條件，如僅限於關在低等、中等安保級監獄內的囚犯申請、犯罪情節較輕、必須證明與性行為對象在服刑前就已是伴侶關係，一旦條件通過，就可獲允許，在單人間裡與伴侶發生性行為。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n獄方人員表示，已有不少表現良好的囚犯成功申請，若是特殊類別的囚犯也想要提出申請，將會面對更多限制條件，但也有一些囚犯成功偽造虛假狀態，以獲得這項特殊獎勵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n維多利亞州政府指出，這項獎勵主要是為了減少囚犯出獄後再犯的可能性，同時降低囚犯家屬的沉重感，除了與伴侶發生性行為外，這些表現良好的囚犯也被允許與其小孩或其他親屬見面。"},{"pid":"2422d7c83e27a909c0a9e2d9cdd16669fdec8235","tid":499741,"uid":54930,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac134aa6324925073fcfb600cf02953aeb7c0ec","tid":499741,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:29:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171214/1072296.htm?t=澳洲囚犯可啪啪啪！獎勵表現良好者%E3%80%80供單人房「開房間」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20171214%2F1072296.htm%3Ft%3D%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E5%9B%9A%E7%8A%AF%E5%8F%AF%E5%95%AA%E5%95%AA%E5%95%AA%EF%BC%81%E7%8D%8E%E5%8B%B5%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E8%80%85%25E3%2580%2580%E4%BE%9B%E5%96%AE%E4%BA%BA%E6%88%BF%E3%80%8C%E9%96%8B%E6%88%BF%E9%96%93%E3%80%8D&d=O1HfhjmKIZ%2BMAfpPFEUQrP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=bff0e3e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171214/1072296.htm?t=澳洲囚犯可啪啪啪！獎勵表現良好者%E3%80%80供單人房「開房間」</a>"},{"pid":"9518b54194f2d36f4e472b42ffb7f3ad135b4b09","tid":499741,"uid":37661,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:30:10.000Z","msg":"首先你要有女"},{"pid":"448b04ab102e1f7ce3c30e47a3a44839071547af","tid":499741,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:32:32.000Z","msg":"美國唔係都一早俾老公老婆扑嘢嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd3c49f312992cb830f6dfa41de7c621541ac2e","tid":499741,"uid":22675,"like":39,"dislike":5,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:57:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國唔係都一早俾老公老婆扑嘢嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n澳洲"},{"pid":"f7915c8e48982e13e3421d244026d348614a9b15","tid":499741,"uid":147242,"like":166,"dislike":3,"score":163,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:01:48.000Z","msg":"覺得唔錯<br />\n為左有得扑野會好乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f23a434e4ac48be37f0cf48f12479f9f65eef9","tid":499741,"uid":45120,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:05:03.000Z","msg":"冇女係咪單人房打飛機<br />\n好似仲空虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd0f42f2cd6e5cf427b9d82c670b467528117aa","tid":499741,"uid":38482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇女係咪單人房打飛機<br />\n好似仲空虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢可能會搵其他囚犯同你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc5eae6a214227a2a66e86b9ce13dec2a24c005","tid":499741,"uid":23170,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,